title: Top 10 One Piece Characters Based on Real People

media:group.media:title: Top 10 One Piece Characters Based on Real People
media:group.media:description:
Turns out Oda gets his inspiration from celebrity culture too! Join Ashley as we look over the characters in One Piece that were based on real-life individuals, including the likes of "Jim Carrey", "Daft Punk", "Tim Curry", and more! Which One Piece character do you think resembles their real world counterpart the most? Let us know in the comments!
